<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in khawvel hi,
 A hehpih bek ziekin;
 A Cha neihsun bawng In sungah,
 Gan kuongah a kuolsak.

[V2]
 Aw Pathien, Na cha hi,
 Gan kuongah a kuol hin;
 Thangvan mipi a ngui zo tam,
 Gan kuong a hun thil um?

[V3]
 2. Keihaw a ding hin chu,
 Gan kuong ka ngaihtuoh un;
 Thasiet leh kipahna luonthi,
 Tui bangin a luong hi.

[V4]
 3. Aw van nuoi mi chengin,
 Gan kuong hi hung en leu;
 A bieng u-ah a luonthi thuongguoh,
 Hawktui bang luong ina.</lyrics>
<title>Gan Kuong Ah</title>
<hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
</song>